@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p>Welcome to ClaimPro, your trusted partner in simplifying the claims process for lecturers.</p>

    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>
        Founded in 2023, ClaimPro emerged from a vision to streamline the claims submission and management process for lecturers. Our founder, Phineas, was inspired to start this business after witnessing firsthand the challenges educators faced in navigating complex reimbursement procedures. Having spent years in academia, Phineas recognized the need for a user-friendly platform that could alleviate the administrative burdens often associated with claiming expenses.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
        At ClaimPro, our mission is to empower lecturers by providing an intuitive, efficient, and transparent claims management system. We strive to ensure that every lecturer can focus on what they do best—teaching—without being bogged down by cumbersome paperwork and lengthy approval processes.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
    <p>
        We envision a world where educators can easily submit and manage their claims, fostering a supportive environment that allows them to thrive. Our platform is designed to facilitate seamless communication between lecturers and administrative staff, ultimately enhancing the educational experience.
    </p>

    <h2>Meet the Founder</h2>
    <p>
        Phineas, a passionate advocate for educators, believes that technology should serve to simplify and enhance the teaching profession. With a background in both education and technology, he combined his expertise to create ClaimPro. Phineas remains committed to continuously improving our platform, ensuring it meets the evolving needs of lecturers and educational institutions.
    </p>

    <h2>Join Us</h2>
    <p>
        We invite you to explore our platform and see how ClaimPro can revolutionize your claims process. Together, we can create a more efficient and supportive environment for lecturers everywhere.
    </p>
</div>

